<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="lo">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <meta name="description" content="ແຜງຄວບຄຸມແອດມິນ - ລົດມືສອງຄຸນນະພາບ">
    <title>ແຜງຄວບຄຸມແອດມິນ</title>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Noto+Sans+Lao:wght@400;600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css">
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
</head>
<body>
    <nav class="navbar navbar-expand-lg navbar-dark bg-primary">
        <div class="container">
            <a class="navbar-brand" href="/admin/dashboard">
                <img src="/images/logo.png" alt="Logo" style="height: 60px; margin-right: 10px;">
                ແຜງຄວບຄຸມແອດມິນ
            </a>
            <button class="navbar-toggler" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#navbarNav" aria-controls="navbarNav" aria-expanded="false" aria-label="Toggle navigation">
                <span class="navbar-toggler-icon"></span>
            </button>
            <div class="collapse navbar-collapse" id="navbarNav">
                <div class="navbar-nav ms-auto">
                    <a class="nav-link active" href="/admin/dashboard">ແຜງຄວບຄຸມ</a>
                    <a class="nav-link" href="/admin/manage-car">ຈັດການລົດ</a>
                    <a class="nav-link" href="/admin/add-car">ເພີ່ມລົດ</a>
                    <a class="nav-link" href="/admin/manage-sell-requests">ຈັດການຄຳຂໍຂາຍ</a>
                    <a class="nav-link" href="/admin/logout">ອອກຈາກລະບົບ</a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </nav>

    <div class="container mt-4">
        <h1 class="text-center">ແຜງຄວບຄຸມແອດມິນ</h1>
        <% if (typeof error !== 'undefined' && error) { %>
            <div class="alert alert-danger alert-dismissible fade show" role="alert">
                <%- error %>
                <button type="button" class="btn-close" data-bs-dismiss="alert" aria-label="Close"></button>
            </div>
        <% } %>
        <div class="row mt-4">
            <div class="col-md-4 mb-4">
                <div class="card text-center">
                    <div class="card-body">
                        <h5 class="card-title">ຈຳນວນລົດທັງໝົດ</h5>
                        <p class="card-text"><%- typeof totalCars !== 'undefined' ? totalCars : 0 %></p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-4 mb-4">
                <div class="card text-center">
                    <div class="card-body">
                        <h5 class="card-title">ຄຳຂໍຂາຍທີ່ລໍຖ້າ</h5>
                        <p class="card-text"><%- typeof pendingRequests !== 'undefined' ? pendingRequests : 0 %></p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-4 mb-4">
                <div class="card text-center">
                    <div class="card-body">
                        <h5 class="card-title">ລົດພຣີມຽມ</h5>
                        <p class="card-text"><%- typeof premiumCars !== 'undefined' ? premiumCars : 0 %></p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <h2 class="text-center mt-5">ສະຖິຕິປະເພດລົດ</h2>
        <div class="row">
            <div class="col-md-3 mb-4">
                <div class="card text-center">
                    <div class="card-body">
                        <h5 class="card-title">ລົດເກົງ</h5>
                        <p class="card-text"><%- typeof sedanCount !== 'undefined' ? sedanCount : 0 %></p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 mb-4">
                <div class="card text-center">
                    <div class="card-body">
                        <h5 class="card-title">ລົດແຮທຊ໌ແບັກ</h5>
                        <p class="card-text"><%- typeof hatchbackCount !== 'undefined' ? hatchbackCount : 0 %></p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 mb-4">
                <div class="card text-center">
                    <div class="card-body">
                        <h5 class="card-title">ລົດກະບະ</h5>
                        <p class="card-text"><%- typeof pickupCount !== 'undefined' ? pickupCount : 0 %></p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 mb-4">
                <div class="card text-center">
                    <div class="card-body">
                        <h5 class="card-title">ລົດຄຣອສໂອເວີ</h5>
                        <p class="card-text"><%- typeof crossoverCount !== 'undefined' ? crossoverCount : 0 %></p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 mb-4">
                <div class="card text-center">
                    <div class="card-body">
                        <h5 class="card-title">ລົດ SUV</h5>
                        <p class="card-text"><%- typeof suvCount !== 'undefined' ? suvCount : 0 %></p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 mb-4">
                <div class="card text-center">
                    <div class="card-body">
                        <h5 class="card-title">ລົດ PPV</h5>
                        <p class="card-text"><%- typeof ppvCount !== 'undefined' ? ppvCount : 0 %></p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 mb-4">
                <div class="card text-center">
                    <div class="card-body">
                        <h5 class="card-title">ລົດ MPV</h5>
                        <p class="card-text"><%- typeof mpvCount !== 'undefined' ? mpvCount : 0 %></p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <footer class="footer text-center bg-dark text-light mt-5">
        <div class="container">
            <p>ທີ່ຢູ່: ນະຄອນຫຼວງວຽງຈັນ, ປະເທດລາວ</p>
            <p>ໂທ: +856 20 1234 5678</p>
            <p>ອີເມວ: contact@yourcarwebsite.com</p>
            <p>ຕິດຕາມພວກເຮົາ:
                <a href="https://www.facebook.com/yourpage" target="_blank" class="text-primary mx-2">Facebook</a>
            </p>
            <p>© 2025 Used Car Sales. ສະຫງວນລິຂະສິດ.</p>
        </div>
    </footer>

    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>
</body>
</html>